  "remarks": "JSC RESEARCH DESIGN BYURO “NOVATOR” is a Russian company engaged in the development, production, operation and repair of long-range anti-aircraft missiles, cruise missiles, anti-ballistic missiles and other warfare equipment. JSC “NOVATOR” provides cruise missile model 3M-54 Kalibr (also known as 3M54-1 Kalibr and 3M14 Biryuza) to the Russian Armed Forces, which is used in the war of aggression against Ukraine.",
